8 SECTION 6. The department of agriculture and biosecurity
9 and department of health shall jointly submit a report to the
10 legislature on the axis deer meat donation pilot program
11 established pursuant to section 159- , Hawaii Revised
12 Statutes, no later than twenty days prior to the convening of
13 each regular session. The report shall include:
14 (1) An update on the implementation and outcomes of the
15 pilot program;
16 (2) The number of participating hunters; charitable,
17 religious, or nonprofit organizations; and processing
18 establishments;
19 (3) Any public health or safety concerns identified;
20 (4) An assessment of current and future resource needs,
21 including staffing requirements; and
