12 SECTION 9. This Act shall take effect upon its approval;
13 provided that:
14 (1) Sections 1 through 6 shall take effect on July 1,
15 2028; and
16 (2) On June 30, 2033, this Act shall be repealed and
17 sections 145D-5, 159-3, and 159-34, Hawaii Revised
18 Statutes, shall be reenacted in the form in which they
